<br>
The only way to fix this that I know of is to have a Dedicated line put in for the refrigerator(I.e. a single feed straight from the circuit box to the outlet that the refrigerator is plugged into). This happens in business alot and is really the best solution. <br>
You COULD try a small office UPS with line filtering and plug the theatre into it...but not sure this would solve the problem, but would cost less than having a dedicated line run. <p><center>Phazy Daayz 52st lvl Disciple<center><br><center>Drunks of Tunare..least till they throw me outa the bar<center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#414141><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/usepnevermore.showPublicProfile?language=EN>SepNevermore</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Runs with Scissors</span><br>  Posts: 101<br> <font color=#CC9900>(8/15/01 2:13:15 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Electrical Question...</span><hr size=1> or you could move the fridge. LAZY AZZZ!~  Lol <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#313532><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/bbrellserilis.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=amanojyaku>Amano Jyaku</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>The Stylin' Hentai Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 1010<br> <font color=#CC9900>(8/15/01 6:39:53 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://people.mn.mediaone.net/timelord81/images/xhead.gif height=83 width=103></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Electrical Question...</span><hr size=1> haha.. But see then I'd actually have to go upstairs to grab a pop. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  @#%$ THAT! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :b --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":b"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  See I'll be watching a movie and I'll be all comfortable and stuff.. I don't wanna take the time to pause the movie and get up and walk upstrais and go to the fridge an